│ incorrect analysis information feeding into it.                                                                                                                   │
│ Here, the *first transformation* means the *first transformation point* that modifies the IR in the pass regardless of whether it's in the `slp-vectorizer`       │
│ module or other modules.                                                                                                                                          │
